<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Astra | Get Started</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to Astra, <%= user.username %>!</h1>
        <p>It looks like your server isn't set up yet. Let's get you running in minutes.</p>
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>Step 1: Verification System</h3>
            <p>Configure how your members join the server. Toggle 2-step verification and set your primary roles.</p>
            <a href="/setup/verification" class="btn">Configure Verification</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>Step 2: Log Systems</h3>
            <p>Keep track of moderation actions and join/leave logs.</p>
            <a href="/setup/logs" class="btn">Configure Logs</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>